snippet.title: Minecraft Dungeons Diaries: Flames of the Nether DLC
snippet.description: The Minecraft Dungeons developers warmly welcome you into the Nether! Discover how they gave Minecraft’s iconic biome a Dungeons twist with new biomes, mobs, and gear! The Flames of the Nether DLC also includes a free update that brings you Gilded items, Ancient Hunts, and a dashing new Piglin Merchant with a penchant for Gold.
